<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Apollonopolis Magna</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><g type="stauros"/> ἀπέκαμον γράφων παρενοχλῶν τοῖς θεοφυλάκτοις καὶ <expan>μεγαλ<ex cert="high">ο</ex>π<ex cert="high">ρεπεστάτοις</ex></expan> ὑμῖν περὶ τῶν γοναχίων, καὶ οὐδὲν ἤνυσα εἰ μὴ τὰ χαρτία 

    <lb n="2"/>ἅπερ δαπανῶ. καὶ αἰσχύνομαι καθάπα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ξ</supplied> γράφων ὑμῖν περὶ τούτου, διότι, ὡς βλέπω, τὸ πρᾶγμα οὐκ ἀρέσκει ὑμῖν. 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ πρὸ τοῦ ἐμὲ γὰρ κατελθεῖν ἐκ τῶν ἄν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ω</supplied>, ἐδεξάμην μίαν <num value="1"/> ἐπιστολὴν ὑμῶν περιέχουσαν ὡς εἰς τὰ ἱστάριά <choice><corr>ἐστιν</corr><sic>εισιν</sic></choice>. παρακαλῶ οὖν 

    <lb n="4"/>ὑμᾶς, εἴπερ ἰσχύει ἡ παράκλησίς μου, πεμφθῆναί μοι αὐτὰ διὰ Σεργίου 

τοῦ στρατιώτου. ἀσπάζομαι δὲ ὑμᾶς διὰ τοῦ <expan>γράμμ<ex cert="high">ατος</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="5"/>τῷ <expan>θεοφυλ<ex cert="high">άκτῳ</ex></expan> μου <expan>δεσπό<ex cert="high">τῃ</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">καὶ</ex></expan> <expan>πατρ<ex cert="high">ὶ</ex></expan> Παπᾷ τῷ <expan>μεγ<ex cert="high">ίστῳ</ex></expan> <expan>παγ<ex cert="high">άρ</ex>χ<ex cert="high">ῳ</ex></expan> <expan>Ἀπόλ<ex cert="high">λωνος Ἄνω</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> Κολλοῦθος <expan>ν<ex cert="high">ο</ex>τ<ex cert="high">άριος</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.20255" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20255" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0676" notBefore="0675" precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 675 - 676 (?)</date></p><p><date notAfter="0661" notBefore="0660" precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 660 - 661 (?)</date></p></div><div n="meta.20255" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Alternativdatierung: ca. 660 - 661. Zur Datierung vgl. ZPE 49, 1982, S. 88.</p></div><div n="meta.20255" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Apoll.</title><biblScope type="numbers">50</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">20255</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0061</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">50</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0061;;50" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20255" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">8